<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div class="container">
<div class="header">
<h1>Membership Terminated</h1>
</div>

<p>Dear {{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

<p>This email is to formally notify you that your membership with {{{Recipient.Account_Name__c}}}, which is expired on {{{Recipient.Active_Membership_End_Date__c}}},&nbsp;{{{Recipient.Active_Membership_Type__c}}} has not been renewed within the 90-day grace period.</p>

<p>As a result, your account and all associated benefits have now been officially terminated.</p>

<p>If you have already renewed your membership, please disregard this email.</p>

<div class="footer">
<p>Best regards,<br />
{{{Organization.Name}}}<br />
Phone: {{{Organization.Phone}}}</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>